San_Clemente.KSBR:
For 88.5 FM in Los Angeles, see KCSN
KSBR is a non-commercial radio station in Mission Viejo, California, broadcasting to the Orange County, California, area on 88.5 FM. KSBR airs an adult album alternative format branded as "The new 88.5 FM". KSBR is a simulcast to KCSN in Northridge, California.


== History ==
KSBR signed on in 1975 as a Class D, 10-watt student-run station and a limited coverage area of only a few miles from the campus of Saddleback Community College.
